{"tid":1944111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】觀塘紀律部隊宿舍有外傭初步確診 住客不滿遲遲未公佈","createTime":"2020-03-26T07:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T16:25:29.000Z","uid":13663,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"47b83856824ab6562f0e8931eeb69fe255194e51","tid":1944111,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:28:58.000Z","msg":"2020.03.26<br />\n將軍澳道觀塘紀律部隊宿舍一座有居民投訴，指居於上址一名新來港外傭據悉日前初步確診武漢肺炎，聘用她的僱主是海關人員，有關海關家庭因此需要隔離14天。居民不滿大廈管理公司及政府部門遲遲未有公開事件，亦未有通知同座甚至同層住客，質疑有隱瞞的嫌疑，又認為若住戶因此而鬆懈恐有感染之虞，促當局正視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200326/2GJVNZSVXC5P5FMQ2KCV6Q6SHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200326%2F2GJVNZSVXC5P5FMQ2KCV6Q6SHM%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=fe9b4944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200326%2F2GJVNZSVXC5P5FMQ2KCV6Q6SHM%2F&h=9bc8b850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200326/2GJVNZSVXC5P5FMQ2KCV6Q6SHM/</a>"},{"pid":"b310df97bad0e99c8027be9a3a06f7ae5aee09a3","tid":1944111,"uid":49208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好得人驚呀"},{"pid":"40defac8497aaef66cfdbdf4bd4bb94a694f7176","tid":1944111,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"聘用她的僱主是海關人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2f220f78ad84428e4a891e1a70597eaec6b695","tid":1944111,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40defac8497aaef66cfdbdf4bd4bb94a694f7176","tid":1944111,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"聘用她的僱主是海關人員<img src=\"/assets/